name: Crescent Seafood Dumplings
description: 20 dumplings with seafood filling. The traditional delicacy from the Far East loved by multiple generations. Uncooked product. Steam 15 minutes until cooked. Ingredients: Prawns, Wheat flour, Cuttlefish, White fish, Vegetable, Garlic, Cereal binder, Salt, Corn flour, Oyster sauce, Sugar, Spices, Soya sauce, Sesame oil, Permitted Acidulants (E330).*Images for illustration purposes only. Product received may vary.
